Melt butter on medium-high in 12-inch nonstick skillet. Add garlic and Simply Potatoes(R). Spread Simply Potatoes(R) into thin layer. Cook for 5 to 6 minutes. Turn Simply Potatoes(R); continue cooking 4 to 5 minutes until potatoes are tender. Reduce heat to medium-low. Spread Simply Potatoes(R) into thin layer. Top with spinach and tomatoes; sprinkle with seasoned salt. Pour Better'n Eggs(R) evenly over mixture in skillet. Cook for 10 to 12 minutes or until eggs are almost set. Heat broiler. Wrap handle of skillet with aluminum foil. Broil 4 to 6 inches from heat for 3 minutes. Top with cheese; broil 30 seconds or until cheese is melted. Cut into wedges.